properties.comment: 25/1/2006 RM All labels, descriptions and units for variables are exactly as given in the technical documentation for the VB, spreadsheet version. Sometimes the descriptions and units are rather dubious: e.g. Monthly transpiration rate in current period (mm) probably should be Transpiration rate (mm.month-1) (since month is the basic unit of time). 16/6/2010 JM The timestep MUST be 1 and the time unit is 1 month.
